definitions.definition: To heat something after it has cooled off, especially previously cooked food ( also in figurative senses ).
To become hot again after having cooled off ( also in figurative senses ).

main_definition: ( transitive ) To heat something after it has cooled off, especially previously cooked food ( also in figurative senses ).
secondary_definitions: ( intransitive ) To become hot again after having cooled off ( also in figurative senses ).
